{"word":"ἀπαγγελία","slug":"ἀπαγγελία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαγγελία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀπαγγέλλω'><el>ἀπαγγέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a report</i>, as of an ambassador, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a narrative, recital</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}